# --- Rust / Cargo ---
# Compiled build artifacts. Large and fully reproducible from source.
/target/

# Backup files created by `cargo fix` / rustfmt edits.
**/*.rs.bk

# NOTE: Cargo.lock is intentionally committed — this crate is an application
# (binary/game), not a library, so a pinned dependency set is desirable.

# --- wasm-bindgen output ---
# Regenerated by the `wasm-bindgen` build step. Ignore it so the generated
# glue + .wasm aren't tracked. If you deploy via GitHub Pages and want the
# artifacts committed, delete this section (or force-add ./pkg).
/pkg/

# --- Claude Code ---
# Machine-local settings & any local memory/scratch. The shared, checked-in
# config (.claude/settings.json) is NOT ignored.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/*.local.json
.claude/memory/

# --- Node (serve.js is dependency-free, but just in case) ---
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*

# --- Editors / IDEs ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- OS cruft ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- OS junk ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
